task.summary: Study: Catch FileExistsError for method set_up_input
Various changes of which I was too lazy to record them.
Initial git commit. Code is still messy.

#1 Added argument 'sort_comp' to Study.set_up_input, which allows the user to sort the directories by composition. #2 Changed the facetsetup.py to make use of this. #3 Changed the facetsetup.py so that it needs a command line argument to the POSCAR file which is to be used for setting up the calculations.

#1 Added path.py, but with a barebone structure. Might not even use it if I can use the pymatgen NEBanalysis module. #2 Changed some small things in facetsym.py, facetsetup.py and study.py. Mainly format-related and TODO's.

#1 Removed currently unused method 'add_restraint' on study. #2 Added symmops as a property to the Cage class. #3 Added the append method to the Cage class, to overwrite the one from Molecule. The idea is that the symmops need to be calculated again. #4 Implemented the 'find_facet_paths' method of the Cage class.

#1 Added the pathsetup.py script, which we will use to setup the pathway NEB calculations to study the energy barriers of Li on the cage molecules. NOTE: This is still only a very rough framework
#2 Added a TODO to the facetsym script

#1 'facetsym.py' Made the class Facet a SiteCollection and MSONable, implementing some of the necessary methods, but not all. #2 Added the script 'checkcalc.py', which checks if a nwchem calculation has finished with an error.
#1 Written a bunch of methods for Facet that allow it to be written to a json file. #2 Started working on a test suite. Will add more tests as I go along.

#1 Changed the find_surface_facets method of the Cage class to allow a more general list of elements which should be ignored in the search for the surface facets. #2 Added a class method from_molecule to the Cage class #3 Created a cage.utils module, which will serve to hold small functions that we need in the main modules. #4 Implemented the facetLandscape.py script
Changes: #1 Large reorganisation of the facetsetup.py script. Also added functionality to study carbon containing cage molecules. #2 Changed the __init__.py for the cage and scripts module.
